NEW += '                        &bull; <strong>Subtree size / sum / max</strong> &mdash; Stage 1 | O(n) | post-order DFS | dp[v] = val[v] + &sum; dp[child]<br>\n'
NEW += '                        &bull; <strong>Tree diameter</strong> &mdash; Stage 1 | O(n) | DFS returning (max_arm, diameter) | global updated at each node<br>\n'
NEW += '                        &bull; <strong>Depth / height</strong> &mdash; Stage 1 | O(n) | DFS | simplest single-value<br><br>\n'
NEW += '                        <strong>Group 2 &mdash; Two-State DP (Binary Choice):</strong><br>\n'
