NEW += '                        &bull; <strong>Domination on Tree</strong> &mdash; Stage 3 | O(n) | dp[v][0/1/2] | three-state covering<br><br>\n'
NEW += '                        <strong>Group 4 &mdash; Rerooting DP (Two-Pass):</strong><br>\n'
NEW += '                        &bull; <strong>Sum of Distances in Tree</strong> &mdash; Stage 2 | O(n) | two-pass DFS; ans[v] = ans[parent] &plusmn; delta | canonical rerooting<br>\n'
