NEW += '                        &bull; <strong>DP on virtual tree</strong> &mdash; Stage 5 | O(k log n) per query | extract virtual tree on k key nodes<br><br>\n'
NEW += '                        <strong>Group 9 &mdash; Interval DP Disguised as Tree DP:</strong><br>\n'
NEW += '                        &bull; <strong>Optimal binary search tree</strong> &mdash; Stage 4 | O(n&sup3;) na&iuml;ve, O(n&sup2;) Knuth | dp[i][j] = cost of BST on keys i..j<br>\n'
NEW += '                        &bull; <strong>Burst Balloons</strong> &mdash; Stage 4 | O(n&sup3;) | final burst in range = root of implicit tree\n'
NEW += '                    </div>\n'
