NEW += '                        Base: dp[leaf][1] = val[leaf], dp[leaf][k] = &minus;INF for k &ne; 1<br>\n'
NEW += '                        Complexity: O(n&sup2;) via pairs-at-LCA; O(n) space if child DPs discarded after merge<br><br>\n'
